2026-05-03T23:23:32.2490694Z               "message": "Document environment variable configuration\n\nAdds docs/configuration.md describing all Ednsv.Web config keys\n(DataDir, CacheTtlHours, DnsServer, Trace, MaskTrace, MaskSalt,\nEnableSmtp/Http/Dnsbl probes, AuthTokenHash, etc.), with a\ndedicated section on enabling Trace logging without turning on the\nverbose Microsoft.AspNetCore default logs by raising only the\nProgram and Ednsv.Web log categories to Debug.\n\nExcludes documentation contributions from CI and the Docker build\ncontext: paths-ignore for docs/ and *.md in the workflow, plus\ndocs/ and **/*.md in .dockerignore.",
