2026-05-03T23:23:32.2511746Z               "id": "5b4c3af11d29f15fc74c6c88a33e83510b38a87b",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2514754Z               "message": "Push Docker images for PR and branch builds with descriptive tags\n\nTag scheme:\n  latest        → default branch only (release pointer, unchanged)\n  latest-any    → every successful build (rolling tip across main/branches/PRs)\n  branch-<name> → push events on any branch (was bare branch name)\n  pr-<number>   → same-repo PR builds (newly enabled for push)\n  sha-<short>   → every build (immutable, content-addressable)\n\nPR builds from forks still build for verification but do not push, since\nGITHUB_TOKEN cannot write to GHCR from a forked PR. The push gate is\ncomputed once at the top of the docker job and reused by both the GHCR\nlogin and build-push steps.",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2516965Z               "timestamp": "2026-05-01T03:44:39Z",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2517278Z               "tree_id": "2170e8437958f10a9d14b07d0103f2e12ad57a8e",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2517757Z               "url": "https://github.com/pkinerd/ednsv/commit/5b4c3af11d29f15fc74c6c88a33e83510b38a87b"
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2518163Z             },
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2518327Z             {
