2026-05-03T23:23:32.2540007Z               "id": "beae99682f2ec5c7613d87a397bd49cdd0705b8e",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2544921Z               "message": "Domain combo: show full known-domain list + add KnownDomains config\n\nThe validator page previously used a native <datalist> for autocomplete,\nwhich the browser silently filters as you type — so you couldn't see the\nfull list of remembered domains once anything was in the field.\n\nReplaced with a small custom combo: an input + ▾ button that opens a\nsuggestions panel showing the full union of:\n  • Recent           — client-side localStorage history (with × to remove)\n  • Known domains    — new operator-curated list from server config\n  • Per-domain DKIM  — domains with config.json DKIM overrides\n\nThe list is always the full union — typing in the input no longer hides\nentries. Open via the ▾ button, focusing the input, Alt+ArrowDown, or F4;\nclose with Escape, click outside, or click an entry. mousedown on entries\nbeats input blur so clicks land cleanly.\n\nAppConfig.KnownDomains: simple list of bare domains, normalised\n(lowercased, trailing dot stripped, blanks dropped, deduped) and persisted\nto config.json. Exposed via /api/defaults alongside perDomainDkimSelectors.\nEditable from the Config page as a comma/space/newline-separated textarea\nmirroring the Default DKIM Selectors UI.",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2548986Z               "timestamp": "2026-05-01T06:03:17Z",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2549301Z               "tree_id": "afcf5aadfa69280fcbef146d49b832b944f58119",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2549773Z               "url": "https://github.com/pkinerd/ednsv/commit/beae99682f2ec5c7613d87a397bd49cdd0705b8e"
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2550185Z             },
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2550354Z             {
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2550530Z               "author": {
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2550757Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2551034Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2551351Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2551574Z               },
