2026-05-03T23:23:32.2575878Z               "message": "Document HTTP/HTTPS proxy env vars\n\nAdds a section to docs/configuration.md explaining that HttpProbeService\nalready honors the standard .NET proxy env vars (no code change needed),\nwhich env vars to set on Linux/macOS/Docker (HTTPS_PROXY, http_proxy\nlowercase, NO_PROXY, ALL_PROXY), authenticated proxy URL form, the\nWindows behaviour difference (uses WinHTTP/IE settings, not env vars),\nand the proxy's scope (HTTP only — does not cover DNS, SMTP, or\ndirect-to-IP nameserver probes; use EnableDirectDns for those).\n\nDocuments the well-known httpoxy gotcha: uppercase HTTP_PROXY is\nintentionally ignored on Unix; lowercase http_proxy must be used for\nplain HTTP.",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2578070Z               "timestamp": "2026-05-01T07:16:42Z",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2578368Z               "tree_id": "4805a58f2405191565636acfbfb606286d40777e",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2578804Z               "url": "https://github.com/pkinerd/ednsv/commit/8ef327d7f89fc948722a7413a65840a06222756d"
