2026-05-03T23:23:32.2582238Z               "id": "48ac462d8571c2efe9dbbbb481b7bdcaa56992dd",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2587344Z               "message": "Add DNS-over-HTTPS path for the propagation check\n\nAdds an opt-in DoH path that routes the public-resolver propagation\ncheck (Google + Cloudflare) over HTTPS through HttpProbeService instead\nof raw UDP/53. Goes through HTTPS_PROXY when set, so this is the\nintended escape hatch for environments that block raw DNS egress but\npermit a forward proxy. The auth-NS direct checks (lame delegation,\nSOA serial, glue, parent delegation, AXFR) have no JSON-DoH equivalent\nand remain gated by EnableDirectDns.\n\nPlumbed end-to-end:\n- AppConfig.EnableDoh + ValidationOptions.EnableDoh, env var EnableDoh,\n  AND-merge in both validation endpoints, exposed via /api/defaults.\n- Web Config page: new \"DNS-over-HTTPS for propagation check\" checkbox.\n- Validator page: matching per-validation checkbox, persisted in\n  localStorage, defaults from /api/defaults like the other toggles.\n- CLI: --doh flag (and --no-direct-dns; --restricted-network now also\n  implies --no-direct-dns).\n- DnsPropagationCheck: when DoH is on, queries dns.google/resolve and\n  cloudflare-dns.com/dns-query (JSON variant via ?ct=application/dns-json),\n  parses the Answer array, normalises MX \"<pref> <host>\" to \"pref:host\",\n  preserves the existing consistency comparison logic. Tracks per-resolver\n  reachability so an all-DoH-blocked run reports Warning rather than a\n  spurious \"consistent\" pass on two empty result sets.\n- docs/configuration.md: new EnableDoh row + scope notes.\n- Quad9 isn't included in the DoH path (no JSON DoH endpoint); raw UDP/53\n  to all three is still used when EnableDoh=false.",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2592711Z               "timestamp": "2026-05-01T07:28:42Z",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2593027Z               "tree_id": "034840f9ef444b5afe795233508107cd878d8ee2",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2593607Z               "url": "https://github.com/pkinerd/ednsv/commit/48ac462d8571c2efe9dbbbb481b7bdcaa56992dd"
