2026-05-03T23:23:32.2613020Z               "id": "f4e5ac3051c8cc054ce10ec03ea036a2df322fae",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2615111Z               "message": "/api/debug/proxy: actually fetch the URL and report status/headers\n\nProxy resolution alone tells you \"what HttpClient would do\"; this adds\n\"what actually happened\" — real status code, response headers, body\nsize, elapsed time, and the underlying exception when the request never\nproduced a response. Makes the (HTTP 0) cases self-diagnosing: a\nSocketException points at DNS or unreachable proxy; a TLS error points\nat interception; a 407 points at proxy auth.",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2616737Z               "timestamp": "2026-05-01T07:55:53Z",
2026-05-03T23:23:32.2617063Z               "tree_id": "1a527e69ab858e2ffee097ba234eafabc0c538ab",
